    public class UiToggleButtons<T>
extends UiMultiSelectionButtonGroup<T,UiToggleButtons<T>>
    A group of buttons that have a selection state that can be toggled independent from each other (similar to check boxes). The datatype defines the type of the button labels. Typically string and enum values are supported.
